      <title>内塔尼亚胡离开医院参加投票，联盟成员持不同意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/netanyahu-leaves-hospital-to-vote-as-coalition-members-dissent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡不顾医生的建议离开医院，前往议会对一项旨在资助国家战争的法案进行投票，但该法案未能获得整个联盟的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/netanyahu-leaves-hospital-to-vote-as-coalition-members-dissent</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 15:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储重新考虑降息 推动美元上涨 创九年来最佳年景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/dollar-gains-as-fed-rate-cut-rethink-fuels-best-year-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济强劲以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的减税和关税政策有望维持高利率，美元周二上涨，创下近十年来最强劲的年度涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/dollar-gains-as-fed-rate-cut-rethink-fuels-best-year-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 14:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
